Abdomen.
Mostly dark yellow, sternites 1–5 paler, tergites 2–5 with anterior dark brown bands laterally. Setae on tergites black, those on hind margin of segments 1–5 longer. Tergite 5 brown, covered by fine white setae with yellow hind margin; sternite 5 brown, with strong triangular ventral projection. Tergite 6 brown and bare. Tergite 7 brown, sternite 7 yellowish, bare. Sternite 8 brown. 
